I do not think it will be a problem for your baggage to be checked in for your whole journey, but they will be able to tell you for sure once you check in at the airport. 
Have a pleasant journey!

@YolyJolly Hi,
A voucher can be used to book flights and extra services such as baggage and seating. It can not be used for hotels or cars.

The voucher need to be used before it expires, but the trip you book can be after the expiration date of the voucher.

Regards,
Peter
